{"tid":659251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國陣失五州政權 馬來西亞變天在望","createTime":"2018-05-09T16:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T21:50:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9a8b3e72d31266bfb4a990ab1054867893b007","tid":659251,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"第14屆馬來西亞大選結束，現時各個票站正在點票階段。多個選區的選情都十分激烈，截至5月9日晚上11點30分，在野希望聯盟贏得的國會議席暫時領先執政國民陣線，而希盟的普選票亦已領先，國陣多個州政權亦岌岌可危，據報，除了反對派本身執政的雪蘭莪、檳城，森美蘭、柔佛、馬六甲、霹靂、吉打州原本的國陣政權倒台。"},{"pid":"e9acad1a63a1746781e99c48a5a404caf6ada480","tid":659251,"uid":4713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"等睇點點下停電"},{"pid":"62cbc1c8489e29fbb4be4dfd6d93a51615e2c4f6","tid":659251,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9acad1a63a1746781e99c48a5a404caf6ada480","tid":659251,"uid":4713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"等睇點點下停電"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"又同一招？"},{"pid":"1462f938a53aed0d8f540b77ca35b167eb84ba90","tid":659251,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞9日舉行國會大選投票，又碰上停電。中國報報導，瓜雪大街一帶從下午6時許開始電流中斷，瓜雪國席瓜雪室內體育館計票中心、武吉美拉華蒂州議席位於直落比艾（Teluk Piai）宗教小學投票站也受影響。<br />\n<br />\n該投票站於下午6時開始計票時，發生停電事故，也受波及，大街一帶連紅綠燈也受影響。據公正黨瓜雪區部執委依斯干達在接受電訪時說，停電於今日下午6時10分發生直至近8時，供電都沒有恢復。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，瓜雪室內體育館剛好是計票中心，他們也擔心會影響到計票活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3133558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3133558&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2Fof7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f59947f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3133558</a>"},{"pid":"72f5d097f7e61c02b3bf85725ebcddb989810bf8","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"邊邊親中？要撐對家"},{"pid":"159fff3024d8b581d2abc9c35f641dc958ca3ade","tid":659251,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1462f938a53aed0d8f540b77ca35b167eb84ba90","tid":659251,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞9日舉行國會大選投票，又碰上停電。中國報報導，瓜雪大街一帶從下午6時許開始電流中斷，瓜雪國席瓜雪室內體育館計票中心、武吉美拉華蒂州議席位於直落比艾（Teluk Piai）宗教小學投票站也受影響。<br />\n<br />\n該投票站於下午6時開始計票時，發生停電事故，也受波及，大街一帶連紅綠燈也受影響。據公正黨瓜雪區部執委依斯干達在接受電訪時說，停電於今日下午6時10分發生直至近8時，供電都沒有恢復。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，瓜雪室內體育館剛好是計票中心，他們也擔心會影響到計票活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3133558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3133558&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2Fof7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f59947f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3133558</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"屌真係"},{"pid":"c303de602691dc564e96e54357e6f13d293f38d5","tid":659251,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"馬拉黑到仆街算撚數啦"},{"pid":"1126bb72a6510f1a53924c13f71542f6c5f43073","tid":659251,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"唔好拎馬拉大選黎打j"},{"pid":"3652c6760042a488ea5bbcaa7f03bdbb6df9ed05","tid":659251,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"72f5d097f7e61c02b3bf85725ebcddb989810bf8","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"邊邊親中？要撐對家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"both 親中"},{"pid":"2b513280870ab1ce935b359793ee358691686b39","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3652c6760042a488ea5bbcaa7f03bdbb6df9ed05","tid":659251,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"72f5d097f7e61c02b3bf85725ebcddb989810bf8","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"邊邊親中？要撐對家"},"citedBy":1,"r