tedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"希望反中喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"舊舊人 馬哈地&middot;穆罕默德 92歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊人 安華 70歲 <br />\n<br />\n2008年7月，安華前助理賽夫報警指控安華，稱遭安華雞姦8次，最後一次事發是在2008年6月26日，在吉隆坡白沙羅一間公寓內被雞姦。8月，安華在吉隆坡大使路法庭被控肛交，他否認罪名，獲准以2萬令吉自行擔保，外出候審。<br />\n<br />\n舊人 納吉&middot;阿都&middot;拉薩 64歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d300e831205bbfddfa79820182b7c6c2bdd77a00","tid":659251,"uid":164383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c303de602691dc564e96e54357e6f13d293f38d5","tid":659251,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"馬拉黑到仆街算撚數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689bda332ed611c4240a3e73c7e2eaa8a47cb71a","tid":659251,"uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c303de602691dc564e96e54357e6f13d293f38d5","tid":659251,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"馬拉黑到仆街算撚數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"香港唔見得有幾白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd85906d4745d83f490a9fb6a426c8273efbce96","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5e116e57a30c629ded5923143aaf2ad73b7da25","tid":659251,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b513280870ab1ce935b359793ee358691686b39","tid":659251,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3652c6760042a488ea5bbcaa7f03bdbb6df9ed05","tid":659251,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"both 親中"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17